snippet.title: 22 Seconds (Ketchapp)
snippet.description:
Play iOS ➡ https://itunes.apple.com/app/22-seconds/id1202904989?mt=8?at=11lGxL&ct=youtube-22seconds

Play Android ➡ https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ketchapp.game22seconds

You have 22 seconds ! How far can you go?

Swipe the ball and guide it through the level. Advance as far as possible before the timer runs out.

◉ Easy to learn, hard to master
◉ Challenge your friends and the whole world
◉ Unlock 30 new ball designs
